Azure DevOps provides development collaboration tools including high-performance pipelines, free private Git repositories,
configurable Kanban boards, and extensive automated and continuous testing capabilities. 
You can access these tools through our cloud service, Azure DevOps Services, or on-premises platform, Azure DevOps Server 

Azure DevOps includes(PBART):
1. Azure Pipelines
CI/CD that works with any language, platform, and cloud. Connect to GitHub or any Git repository and deploy continuously.
Azure Pipelines helps you implement a build, test, and deployment pipeline for any app.

2. Azure Boards
Powerful work tracking with Kanban boards, backlogs, team dashboards, and custom reporting.

3. Azure Artifacts
Maven, npm, and NuGet package feeds from public and private sources. 

4. Azure Repos

5. Azure Test Plans

